"type":"p",
"hlId":"972bc5",
"class":"test",
"children":[
"A 60-year-old woman has a temperature of 38.8 °C (101.8 °F). Her right thigh is swollen and extremely tender to palpation, with a 5-cm red patch in the middle of the tender area. She requires morphine for pain."
]
},
{
"type":"p",
