]
},
" ",
"For diagnosis, choose myonecrosis. For management, select urgent MRI followed by surgical debridement."
]
},
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"a80d6f",
"class":"test",
"children":[
"A 20-year-old college football player has a fever, furuncles, and associated cellulitis."
